Subject: [PATCH 9/9] Implement GlobalProtect NLB ESP envelope

Wire the 16-byte NLB UDP envelope around ESP ciphertext for GlobalProtect
gateways: encap/decap in gpst_nlb.c, hooks in esp.c, 56-byte NLB probes,
and keepalive-before-data in gpst_esp_send_probes().
